{"tid":2233611,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★數碼人民幣料最快2022年推出","createTime":"2020-10-07T09:06:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T03:16:57.000Z","uid":19454,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"d27f40482fb4061b52d30b3358b553cd889c4c1f","tid":2233611,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T09:06:31.000Z","msg":"外媒報道，中國人民銀行耗時六年研究的虛擬貨幣──數碼人民幣，在經過一連串實際測試後，市場預計最快可望在2022年面世。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述中國人民銀行數字貨幣研究所所長穆長春表示，數碼貨幣的功能和屬性跟紙鈔完全一樣，只不過它的形態是數碼化。內媒則報道，數碼人民幣的目的是為了替換掉部分紙鈔，與市面上流通的人民幣等值兌換，並不會增加貨幣總數量。數碼人民幣除了可帶來一般電子支付的便利外，「雙離線」技術是一大亮點，意即就算手機在沒有網絡信號之下，收付雙方面還是能進行交易。<br />\n<br />\n穆長春描述，只要兩部手機上均設有數碼人民幣的數碼錢包，有沒有網絡都不重要，只需將兩個手機「碰一碰」，就能把一個人數碼錢包裏的數碼貨幣轉給另一個人。<br />\n另一方面，與一般電子支付工具不同的是，數碼人民幣不用與傳統銀行帳戶綁定，使用方式如用紙鈔消費一樣，只要在不違法的情況下，都能滿足消費者匿名的需求，同時也打破不同支付工具不能相互轉帳的限制。<br />\n<br />\n由於中國民眾早已習慣電子支付的交易方式，預計數碼人民幣推出後不會產生太大適應性的問題。穆氏強調，內地推出數碼人民幣目的並不是要取代支付寶與微信，同時數碼人民幣的推出也不會影響兩者應用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201007/bkn-20201007153443946-1007_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20201007%2Fbkn-20201007153443946-1007_00842_001.html&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmdey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=08c63560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201007/bkn-20201007153443946-1007_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"99e4fdf75eee9dc6c8a7cc24ad7f91f62e740587","tid":2233611,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T09:06:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ddc4f41ee3d0ff1337c59b975217f378181a59","tid":2233611,"uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T09:07:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/HarshAmazingIrishwaterspaniel-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FHarshAmazingIrishwaterspaniel-size_restricted.gif&h=0a7ebb2c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29409d3c3bea19a0ec4f0468bca06e681cfdc9a4","tid":2233611,"uid":127905,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T09:10:59.000Z","msg":"「雙離線」技術是一大亮點，意即就算手機在沒有網絡信號之下，收付雙方面還是能進行交易。<br />\n穆長春描述，只要兩部手機上均設有數碼人民幣的數碼錢包，有沒有網絡都不重要，只需將兩個手機「碰一碰」<br />\n<br />\n舊手機NFC 都冇 data network 又話唔洗 用bluetooth 又唔洗碰一碰<br />\n究竟係咩技術?"},{"pid":"09d86f087e78834e8d0313fc4bc50399dc2561b4","tid":2233611,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T09:12:27.000Z","msg":"數佢老母"},{"pid":"9c66abdd60194da704153fd0f0cec6f2b530da02","tid":2233611,"uid":132810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T09:13:00.000Z","msg":"咩都要數碼化<br />\n冷HI TECH"},{"pid":"985cf62e623020d136b6087ff0891ac2577b3356","tid":2233611,"uid":4811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T09:13:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a817040fb106fd8f1e01c25b5161464248823c88","tid":2233611,"uid":50737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T09:14:27.000Z","msg":"回血劍<br />\n<br />\n貪污果啲現金gg了"},{"pid":"58f8d50f14fe186baa21698c1e66695af5040adc","tid":22